A former air hostess says she now identifies as a black “African woman” after undergoing controversial tanning injection treatment. Martina , from Germany,was born blonde-haired and light-skinned. Martina bizarrely decided she wanted to change her ethnicity, vowing to get “darker and darker and see what the limits are.” Thanks to a new medical procedure in the US, the ex-flight attendant has darkened her skin. Martina said: “I’m so happy and proud to be a real African woman.”  Martina as a white woman  Martina as a black woman